"""Adaptive per-column thickness: use thick=10 unless it disagrees with thick=40.

For each column:
- compute top_thin (thick=10) and top_thick (thick=40)
- if only one valid: use it
- if both valid:
    - if top_thick - top_thin > GAP (e.g., 40µm): thin picked a thin AF band,
      use top_thick instead
    - else: both agree, use top_thin (preserves clean-subject pia edge)
"""
